.pytest_cache/
docs/
README.md

# Exclude the heavy generated artifacts individually rather than excluding
# `data/` wholesale and re-including with `!`. Negating a path inside an
# already-excluded directory is fragile, and the failure mode is silent: the
# image builds fine and the CAG route 500s at runtime.
data/corpus/
data/evals/
data/chunks.jsonl
data/*.txt
data/*.out
data/*.err

# data/cag_context.json is deliberately NOT excluded — it is the pre-packed
# CAG prefix (~550 KB) the deployed app needs.
